parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock, making it difficult or impossible to turn, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks or resists turns
excessive force is required to unlock the seized wheel
the vehicle is inoperative
the steering locks up in cold temperatures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering cradle can cause the vehicle to become inoperative, making it difficult or impossible to control, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The left cradle bolt breaks
the right cradle bolt falls through the frame
the vehicle is inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract properly
the seat belt locks the driver in
the seat belt is stuck in a fixed position
the seat belt cannot be adjusted or removed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt plastic cover can cause the seat belt buckle to malfunction, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The plastic cover on the seat belt breaks
the plastic cover on the seat belt buckle pops off
the seat belt buckle is exposed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine cradle bolt can cause the front end of the vehicle to collapse, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The front end of the vehicle collapses
the steering column disintegrates
the vehicle is difficult to steer or control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension system can cause the vehicle to vibrate or wobble, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Poor suspension
shocks absorber failure
vehicle vibration or wobbling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat frame can cause the seat to collapse or break, potentially leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The seat frame breaks
the seat collapses
the seat back breaks and collapses down
the seat becomes unstable.
